{"type":"text","timestamp":1777038220656,"sessionID":"ses_24044ebb0ffe3xc67TJAedk1gX","part":{"id":"prt_dbfbb5ca3001RBfVJAKKVYbLZz","messageID":"msg_dbfbb556c001PJsai1WY3UeQr0","sessionID":"ses_24044ebb0ffe3xc67TJAedk1gX","type":"text","text":"I've created a polished, self-contained Snake game in `index.html`.\n\n### Key Features:\n- **Visuals:** Dark retro aesthetic with smooth colors, rounded snake segments, and a subtle grid.\n- **Controls:** Arrow keys for movement; built-in logic prevents the snake from reversing into itself.\n- **Persistence:** High score is saved to your browser's local storage.\n- **Feedback:** Clear Game Over screen with a restart option.\n\nTo play, simply open the `index.html` file in any modern web browser.","time":{"start":1777038220451,"end":1777038220655}}}
